text.text: How to set mileage rounding for patients?

text: To set mileage rounding for patients, you can click the "Mileage rounding" field and select an option from the list. You can also modify an existing policy or plan by clicking the "Mileage rounding" field and selecting to round up/down or use fractional mileage.

text.text: How to  set mileage rounding for patients who are primary or self-pay payers?

text: To set mileage rounding for patients who are primary or self-pay payers, you can: 1. On the navigation bar, click Settings 2. Click the Configuration tab 3. Scroll down to the "Patient billing" heading 4. Click on the "Mileage rounding" field and then select an option from the list 5. Scroll down and click Save.
